{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/header.png?t=1728928989\" /><br><br><i>What Remains</i> is an eerie visual novel with a truly branching narrative inspired by Ukrainian folklore.<br><br>You wake up to the sound of hooves. Goat, Bear, and Granny invite you to carol in the village in nowhere. It awaits your first choice.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/snowfall.gif?t=1728928989\" /><br><br>To break the silence, you knock on the first door.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/khata_gif.gif?t=1728928989\" /><br><br>Decide the villagers' fate. Save one, condemn another. Prevent someone's insanity or descend into your madness. Set the village in flames or freeze it in a grueling winter.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/extras/wood_with_branches1.gif?t=1728928989\" /><br><br>It's a story about the weight of your whisper, word, and thought. What you do matters, and what you don't matters even more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Go on, dear guest. Make what is the easiest and the hardest to make\u2014choices. </h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728928989","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/page.bg.jpg?t=1728928989","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/c8ee05b280a55a590c1aa889a74ed17933713742/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728928989","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010620/c8ee05b280a55a590c1aa889a74ed17933713742/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728928989","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description